    <PrimAttribute name="locked" id="a6b3c9d7-9417-4e70-ae33-66885acdf8fa">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <text>This is used when painting different attributes on the area. For instance Location Restrictions or Sub Block Stacks.
We show all the existing  Sub Block Stacks, plus buildings and light towers etc. on screen these are locked.
The user then can paint the  Sub Block Stack that is being updated plus any unused locations.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
